Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Falklands surrender
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wvst
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Jun 1982
US may need to reconsider policy towards UK following Falklands surrender. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less